name: SearchResultCollection
description: Contains a collection of [range](range.md) objects as a result of a search operation.

properties.name: first
properties.description: Gets the first searched result in this collection.

methods.name: getItem
methods.description: Gets a range object by its index in the collection.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: A number that identifies the index location of a range object.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
